Global Personal Health Record Tools Market Insights
Personal Health Record Tools Market size was valued at USD 3.8 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 10.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 14.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Personal Health Record Tools Market Overview
The global Personal Health Record (PHR) tools market is experiencing substantial growth, projected to reach a market value of USD 17.3 billion by 2028, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.5% from 2023 to 2028. This growth is driven by the increasing adoption of digital healthcare solutions, the demand for better patient data management, and the shift toward personalized healthcare. As healthcare systems evolve, there is a greater emphasis on improving patient outcomes through the use of technology. The need for secure and efficient management of health records is prompting healthcare providers and patients alike to adopt PHR tools that offer centralized, real-time access to personal health information.

